{"tid":2362437,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚引玉對抗霸權&IT佬入] 轉 AdvertisingID / UUID /DeviceID 令廣告商成效大減","createTime":"2021-01-11T12:25:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T05:33:37.000Z","uid":6145,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3a66ec37da9f2ec9eb3bd80ef6dc5491a2c6b52d","tid":2362437,"uid":6145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:25:09.000Z","msg":"以我所知<br />\n其實FB/Google/廣告商 track 你cross-app activities 都係用你部電話既advertisingID / UUID / DeviceID<br />\n<br />\n如果有方法可以定時轉一轉, 令佢對你既tracking 斷開左<br />\n即使只係三種ID 其中一種<br />\n都令到佢地變跛腳鴨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBig data 又不停loss 你tracking<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢錢又賺少左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廣告商冇辦法變現你既私隱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你條氣都順D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇IT 人comment 幾句<br />\n以上諗法可唔可行？Or 有咩方法做得更完善？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我google 過UUID 搵唔到方法轉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAdvertisingID:<br />\nTo reset your Android advertising ID, Open Google Settings on your Android device by tapping on menu and then on Google Settings once all apps are displayed on the screen. Locate and tap on the Ads menu under Services. Tap on &ldquo;reset advertising ID&rdquo; on the new page.<br />\n<br />\nDeviceID：<br />\nInstall Device ID Changer app and launch it.<br />\nTap on the &ldquo;Random&rdquo; button in the &ldquo;Edit&rdquo; section to generate a random device ID.<br />\nAfterwards, tap on the &ldquo;Go&rdquo; button to immediately change the generated ID with your current one."},{"pid":"4f6093136cc4414b6e68c3495f83ead9ed0e412e","tid":2362437,"uid":6145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:31:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45085ffa6e2892ced28